pullRequest.body:
Makes `FirstOrder.Language.orderStructure` a `def` instead of an instance
Provides `def`s to turn `L.Structure`s in ordered languages modelling the relevant theories into `LE`, `Preorder`, `PartialOrder`, and `LinearOrder`.
